      </para>
      <para id="para-00037">Find the median.</para>
      </problem>
      <solution id="sol-00007">
      <para id="para-00038">Step 1: In order to find the median, we first need to sort the data so that they’re in order, smallest to largest:
      <table summary="." class="unnumbered" id="table-00010">
      <tgroup cols="6">
      <colspec colnum="1" colname="c1" colwidth="1*"/>
      <colspec colnum="2" colname="c2" colwidth="1*"/>
      <colspec colnum="3" colname="c3" colwidth="1*"/>
